  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0da7 \u0db4\u0db1\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba 47\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The country catches 47 who went to jump",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy says that 47 people suspected of trying to illegally migrate to a foreign country by sea were arrested.",
        "Based on information received from the Sri Lanka Navy, the Wennappuwa police conducted a special search operation in Hawennappuwa city, and these suspects were arrested while observing and inspecting 03 suspicious vans.",
        "Among these people, 47 people including 37 men over 18 years of age, 06 women and 04 under 18 years of age have been arrested.",
        "These people were identified as residents of Jaffna, Vavuniya, Trincomalee, Kalmune, Batticaloa, Puttalam, Halawatha, Marawila, Mahawewa, Mundalama and Wellawatta, and the group was handed over to Wennappuwa Police for further investigations."
      ],
